<!--
    strings.xml – Romanian (Română)
    =========================================================================
    This file contains translations for all string resources defined in
    values/strings.xml (the German source of truth). The authoritative
    key set is enforced by LocaleSyncTest.

    TRANSLATION NOTES:
      · WHO / DHS are kept as abbreviations (internationally recognised).
      · BAC (Blood Alcohol Concentration) is rendered in each language's
        preferred term where one exists; otherwise the abbreviation is kept.
      · {name} and {count} in drink_delete_blocked are custom
        substitution placeholders handled by the code (not Android format args).
      · %1$s / %1$d / %1$02d etc. are standard Android format arguments and
        must be preserved verbatim in every translation.
      · &#215; is the multiplication sign ×; keep it as-is.
    =========================================================================
-->
